pective unique journey unique insight we are on a truly unique journey launched in south africa in  we are one of the first asset management firms to build a global franchise from emerging market origins this means we see the world differently allowing our clients to benefit from our unique insight people more than a job we are curious for our clients we put our clients and our people at the centre of our business this is after all their business our people enjoy working without constraints and they’re passionate about what they do that’s why so many of our senior people have been with us for so long featured investment views inflation watch  july  john stopford head of multiasset income at investec asset management discusses inflation and central bank policy in key global markets with lindsay williams listen to podcast natural resources indicator  july  an overview of the natural resources sector read more related links commodities  resource indicator natural resources indicator emerging market debt indicator  july  a review of recent developments in the emerging market debt universe supplemented by specific country and sector commentary read more related links commodities  resource indicator a disinflationary environment  june  philip saunders and lindsay williams discuss inflation and the bond markets listen to podcast brexit talks start  june  john stopford talks to lindsay williams to discuss the impact of brexit as negotiations between the european union and the uk get underway listen to podcast our responsibility to society as longterm asset managers we are deeply aware of our broader responsibility to society we are proud to support a number of initiatives that work with local communities and their environments read more investment institute leveraging our firm’s expertise and a worldwide network of experts we can empower our clients as they navigate an increasingly complex investment landscape read more investment teams introducing our investment model and 