nounced a tenyear title sponsorship of investec test match cricket for the england and wales cricket board on  november  at lords cricket ground this sponsorship will run until  and is the longest sponsorship agreement secured in ecb’s history rugbyedit investec is involved in a number of rugby sponsorships around the world as they feel that rugby embodies investecs beliefs in collaborative teamwork innovative play and determination and it’s for these reasons that we support many rugby initiatives investec previously sponsored the investec internationals series formerly the investec challenge played at twickenham stadium england investec is in the third year as the sponsor of the investec super rugby competition in australia new zealand and south africa investec also supports the international rugby academy south africa which aims to capitalise on an untapped demand for high performance in playing and coaching rugby in south africa in  investec announced that they are the official sponsors of the tri nations rugby competition in new zealand for the second year running horse racingedit investec has become a long term sponsor of the epsom derby festival in the uk until  the illustrious horseracing event is now known as the investec derby investec also sponsors the investec cape derby in south africa footballedit investec has become the official shirt sponsor for tottenham hotspurs domestic cup games and uefa champions league games for the  and uefa europa league games for the  seasons this sponsorship marked the first promotion into the football world for investec in  investec became the official shirt sponsor for widnes fc in the north west counties football league division one promathsedit since  investec has been sponsoring a flagship project started by the kutlwanong centre for math science and technology the project aims at improving the mathematics and science skills of students from historically disadvantaged regions across south africa the project has been a huge success year on year with most of the students obtaining distinctions in mathematics and science and their other subjects in  the project was awarded the mail  guardian investing in the future stem award otheredit other sponsorships include the nelson mandela th birthday tribute in londons hyde park and russian tennis player elena dementieva for the  wimbledon tournament as well as the australian open in january  awardsedit the company was awarded most trusted asset management brand south africa in  by global brands magazine award referencesedit  a b c annual report  pdf retrieved  april    about investec investeccom retrieved  april    brief overview on the salient features of investec’s dual listed companies structure pdf wwwinvesteccom investec retrieved  march    london stock exchange prices londonstockexchangecom  july  retrieved  april    johannesburg stock exchange jsecoza retrieved  april    london stock exchange indices londonstockexchangecom retrieved  april    a b c about investec investeccouk  november  retrieved  april    a b c d e f investec history archived from the original on  october  retrieved  april    investec history current flash applet investeccom  june  retrieved  april    investec enlarges its footprint business times  investec does it the niche way in london business times  investec wealth  investment  home rensburgsheppardscouk retrieved  march    investec buys uks biggest subprime mortgage lender the daily telegraph london  may   investecs australia move sydney morning herald  may   investec buys rensburg for £ million london evening standard  march   investec completes ncb takeover daily business post  june   a b c d e f structure and management investec retrieved  april    a b c financial sector charter report  investec test cricket investeccouk  march  retrieved  april    why investec sponsors the rugby investeccouk  march  retrieved  april    rugby football union clubsrfucom retrieved  april    about the super  supercom sports di