f financial products and services to a client base in three principal markets the united kingdom south africa and australia investec is dual listed on the london stock exchange and the johannesburg stock exchange investec is a ftse  company investecs south african headquarters are at  grayston drive sandown sandton investecs uk headquarters are at  gresham street in central london investecs irish headquarters are at the harcourt building harcourt street in dublin contents  history  operations  products and divisional structure  legal structure  empowerment in south africa  sponsorships  cricket  rugby  horse racing  football  promaths  other  awards  references  external links historyedit investec was founded as a small leasing and financing company in  in johannesburg by larry nestadt errol grolman and ian kantor it has expanded through a combination of organic growth and strategic acquisitions it secured a banking licence in  and was first listed on the jse securities exchange in south africa in  after merging with metboard a trust company in  investec bank limited was restructured into investec group limited igl giving investec management and staff control of the company in  investec acquired property management company i kuper  company pty limited corporate merchant bank limited formerly hill samuel merchant bank limited and trade finance company reichmans limited investec entered the uk market in  by acquiring londonbased allied trust bank limited atb this was the first international acquisition by the group in  investec acquired guinness mahon a leading london based merchant bank and henderson crosthwaite its stockbroking arm for £m it also bought hambros plc another london based merchant bank the same year it was first listed on the london stock exchange in  in  in a black economic empowerment transaction empowerment partners acquired a  stake in the south africalisted investec investec loyal about to win the  sydney to hobart taken from sandy bay hobart tasmania australia in  investec sold its uk private client stockbroking operation carr sheppards crosthwaite limited to rensburg plc investec retains a  interest in the combined entity rensburg sheppards plc in  investec plc acquired kensington group plc and experien pty ltd investec plc acquired the remaining shares in rensburg sheppards plc in  this business has since been rebranded as investec wealth  investments and incorporates other wealth activities previously operated through the bank in june  investec plc completed the € million acquisition of irish brokerage firm ncb as a result investec now employs more than  specialists in ireland operationsedit investec employs approximately  people worldwide and operates primarily in south africa the united kingdom australia and ireland it also has banking operations in switzerland mauritius guernsey hong kong jersey namibia botswana canada taiwan and the united states products and divisional structureedit investec is organised as a network comprising six business divisions asset management wealth  investment property private banking investment banking and capital markets legal structureedit lti tx silver advertising for investec in july  investec became the first south african company to list on both the london and johannesburg stock exchanges by implementing a dual listed companies dlc structure the main features of the dlc structure are investec plc and investec limited are separate legal entities and listings but are bound together by contractual agreements and mechanisms investec plc is the holding company for the majority of the groups nonsouthern african operations and investec limited is the holding company for the majority of the groups southern african operations investec operates as if it is a single unified economic enterprise shareholders have common economic and voting interests as if investec plc and investec limited were a single company creditors however are ringfenced to either investec plc or investec limited as there are no cross guarantees between the companies empowerment in south africaedit investecs approach to transformation within south africa involves fostering the creation of new black entrepreneurial platforms serving as a source of empowerment financing encouraging internal transformation by bringing about greater representivity in the workplace investec focuses on creating black entrepreneurs within its organisation sponsorshipsedit cricketedit investec announced a tenyear title sponsorship of investec test match cricket for the england and wales cricket board on  november  at lords cricket ground this sponsorship will run until  and is the longest sponsorship agreement secured in ecb’s history rugbyedit investec is involved in a number of rugby sponsorships around the world as they feel that rugby embodies investecs beliefs in collaborative teamwork innovative play and determination and it’s for these reasons that we support many rugby initiatives investec previously sponsored the investec internationals series formerly the investec challenge played at twickenham stadium england investec is in the third year as the sponsor of the investec super rugby competition in australia new zealand and south africa investec also supports the international rugby academy south africa which aims to capitalise on an untapped demand for high performance in playing and coaching rugby in south africa in  investec announced that they are the official sponsors of the tri nations rugby competition in new zealand for the second year running horse racingedit investec has become a long term sponsor of the epsom derby festival in the uk until  the illustrious horseracing event is now known as the investec derby investec also sponsors the investec cape derby in south africa footballedit investec has become the official shirt sponsor for tottenham hotspurs domestic cup games and uefa champions league games for the  and uefa europa league games for the  seasons this sponsorship ma